### Orders - Create secure order
# @name createOrder
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/secure
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "restaurantId": {{restaurantId}},
  "receiverAddress": "1 REST Client Street, Ho Chi Minh City",
  "receiverLat": 10.7769,
  "receiverLng": 106.7009,
  "distanceKm": 2.5,
  "baseFee": 20000,
  "discountAmount": 0,
  "taxAmount": 0,
  "shippingType": "STANDARD",
  "idempotencyKey": "order-{{$guid}}",
  "items": [
    {
      "foodId": {{foodId}},
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### Orders - Create order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "restaurantId": {{restaurantId}},
  "receiverAddress": "2 REST Client Street, Ho Chi Minh City",
  "receiverLat": 10.7769,
  "receiverLng": 106.7009,
  "distanceKm": 2,
  "baseFee": 20000,
  "shippingType": "STANDARD",
  "idempotencyKey": "order-{{$guid}}",
  "items": [
    {
      "foodId": {{foodId}},
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

